                " LASL FN tandem Van de Graaff."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A 50 microg/cm2 target of 241Am which had been",
                "prepared by vacuum evaporation onto a 3 mm diam spot",
                "on a 30 microg/cm2 C foil."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EDE",
                "COINC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The direct reaction protons were recorded",
                "with a dE-E counter telescope which consisted of a",
                "300 microm transmission detector and a 2 mm depletion",
                "depth E detector. The telescope was located at 125",
                "with respect to the beam axis. Two 300 mm2 fission",
                "fragment detectors, which were collinear in the",
                "center of mass system, were located at ~90 degrees to",
                "the recoil axis as defined by the counter telescope.",
                "Triple coincidence events were measured between the",
                "two fission detectors and the outgoing proton."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The energies and masses of the coincident fission",
                "fragments were obtained using the \"mass defect\"",
                "calibration procedure. The primary fission",
                "calibration standard was 252Cf."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Neutron correction based on method of Terrell."
              ]
            }
          ],
